<h1>New Wiki Page</h1>

<div class="row">
  <div class="col-md-4">
    <p>Guidelines for wiki entries</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Search Blocipedia in case an article already exists on the subject</li>
      <li>Practice editing already existing articles</li>
      <li>Gather sources</li>
      <li>Must have a unique title.</li>
    </ul>

    <p>Simple Markdown</p>
    <ul>
      <li> <i>Italics:</i> *asterisks* or _underscores_.</li>
      <li> <b>Bold:</b> **two asterisks** or __two underscores__.</li>
      <li> <strike>Strikethrough:</strike>~~two tildas~~ </li>
      <li> Paragraph break: &lt;br> </li>
    </ul>
    <p><%= link_to "More Markdown Syntax", "http://five.squarespace.com/display/ShowHelp?section=Markdown", :target =>"_blank" %></p>

  </div>
  <div class="col-md-8">
    <%= render partial: 'form', locals: { wikipage: @wikipage } %>

  </div>
</div>
